Andy Ruiz Jr and Anthony Joshua pose during the press conference as promoter Eddie Hearn looks on. JOHANNESBURG - Touted as the boxing rematch of the year, Andy Ruiz Jr and Anthony Joshua face each other on Saturday in the Clash On The Dunes. Joshua, a British former champion, lost to Mexican-American Ruiz Jr in New York City in June. Now, he'll try to claim the WBA, IBF, WBO and IBO heavyweight world titles from Ruiz Jr. You can watch the match live, exclusively on Openview. Here are some stats, provided by The Stats Zone. Andy Ruiz Jr vs Anthony Joshua 2 Tale of the Tape. Andy Ruiz Jr vs Anthony Joshua 2 Form Guide. Anthony Joshua vs Andy Ruiz Jr 1 Punch Type. Anthony Joshua vs Andy Ruiz Jr Punch Accuracy.